OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772100321
OL,3,CPatients face 'considerable' wait for
OL,4,Cassisted dying in Isle of Man
OL,6,FA process to get assisted dying on the
OL,7,FIsle of Man's statute book has taken
OL,8,Falmost four times longer than other
OL,9,Fbills, analysis shows.
OL,11,FThe Island's Tynwald became the first
OL,12,Fparliament in the British Isles to
OL,13,Fagree a framework for assisted dying
OL,14,Fin March 2025, but the UK Ministry of
OL,15,FJustice still has not processed the
OL,16,Flegislation for royal assent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
