OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772100321
OL,3,CPatients face 'considerable' wait for
OL,4,Cassisted dying in Isle of Man
OL,6,FA freedom of information (FOI) showed
OL,7,Fthat since the start of 2020, the
OL,8,FMinistry of Justice took an average 88
OL,9,Fdays to process Isle of Man
OL,10,Flegislation.
OL,12,FIt has been over 300 days since the
OL,13,FBill was put to the UK Government.
OL,15,FAfter the Assisted Dying Bill, the
OL,16,Fnext-slowest scrutiny process was in
OL,17,F2021, when the Lord Chancellor
OL,18,Freceived the Climate Change Bill 194
OL,19,Fdays before clearing it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
