PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772100321
OL,3,CPatients face 'considerable' wait for
OL,4,Cassisted dying in Isle of Man
OL,6,FAlex Allinson, who steered the
OL,7,Flegislation through the Tynwald, said
OL,8,F"a lot of work" will be needed once
OL,9,Fthe Bill becomes law, including
OL,10,Fsetting up support systems for
OL,11,Fpatients, families and medical staff
OL,12,Fon the island.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772100321
OL,3,CPatients face 'considerable' wait for
OL,4,Cassisted dying in Isle of Man
OL,6,FHe said: "I think there is the impetus
OL,7,Freally to complete the full passage of
OL,8,Fthis Bill so we can start with some of
OL,9,Fthe implementation of it, which will
OL,10,Ftake a considerable amount of time
OL,11,Fbecause there were various amendments
OL,12,Fand clauses brought into the Bill in
OL,13,Fterms of the implementation, in terms
OL,14,Fof secondary legislation that has to
OL,15,Fgo through the next Tynwald."
OL,26,@wD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772100321
OL,3,CPatients face 'considerable' wait for
OL,4,Cassisted dying in Isle of Man
OL,6,FDr Allinson, a GP and independent
OL,7,Fmember of the House of Keys (MHK),
OL,8,Fadded: "So, there is a lot of work to
OL,9,Fbe done, however, across the world,
OL,10,Fnumerous jurisdictions make available
OL,11,Fassisted dying to their populations."
OL,13,FThe Bill, passed on 25 March 2025,
OL,14,Fwould make assisted dying available to
OL,15,Fterminally ill adults who are
OL,16,F"reasonably expected to die" within 12
OL,17,Fmonths.
OL,19,FThey must have lived on the Isle of
OL,20,FMan for at least five years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772100321
OL,3,CPatients face 'considerable' wait for
OL,4,Cassisted dying in Isle of Man
OL,6,FA UK Government spokesperson said the
OL,7,Flength of processing time "depends on
OL,8,Fthe complexities and sensitivities of
OL,9,Fa bill, as well as any legal and
OL,10,Fconstitutional issues".
OL,12,FThere is no set deadline or target
OL,13,Ftime for Whitehall to process
OL,14,Flegislation approved in Douglas.
OL,16,FDr Allinson said the lack of deadline
OL,17,Fis "interesting".
OL,26,@oD@[OUrD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772100321
OL,3,CPatients face 'considerable' wait for
OL,4,Cassisted dying in Isle of Man
OL,6,FHe said: "We've had two separate
OL,7,Fapproaches now from the Ministry of
OL,8,FJustice regarding some of the
OL,9,Foperational issues of the legislation.
OL,11,F"These don't interfere with our
OL,12,Fconstitutional relationship with the
OL,13,FUnited Kingdom.
OL,15,F"It's quite clear that the Assisted
OL,16,FDying Bill for the Isle of Man is only
OL,17,Ffor Isle of Man residents who have
OL,18,Fbeen resident here for at least five
OL,19,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772100321
OL,3,CPatients face 'considerable' wait for
OL,4,Cassisted dying in Isle of Man
OL,6,F"So, it really is a matter of royal
OL,7,Fassent being granted so that we can
OL,8,Fget on with the significant amount of
OL,9,Fadditional consultation we will need
OL,10,Fto do to bring it into implementation."
OL,12,FResponsibility for processing
OL,13,Flegislation from the Crown
OL,14,FDependencies lies with the Lord
OL,15,FChancellor, a role currently held by
OL,16,FDeputy Prime Minister David Lammy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772100321
OL,3,CPatients face 'considerable' wait for
OL,4,Cassisted dying in Isle of Man
OL,6,FA UK Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"The length of time taken to pass
OL,8,FCrown Dependency legislation depends
OL,9,Fon the complexities and sensitivities
OL,10,Fof a bill, as well as any legal and
OL,11,Fconstitutional issues
OL,13,F"This makes sure legislation is
OL,14,Fproperly considered, in line with our
OL,15,Fgood governance responsibilities."
OL,17,FAn Isle of Man Government spokesperson
OL,18,Fsaid: "The Isle of Man Government
OL,19,Fnotes that the Assisted Dying Bill is
OL,20,Fcurrently progressing through the
OL,21,Froyal assent process.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772100321
OL,3,CPatients face 'considerable' wait for
OL,4,Cassisted dying in Isle of Man
OL,6,F"We are not able to comment on the
OL,7,Ftimelines of that process, which are a
OL,8,Fmatter for the UK Ministry of Justice.
OL,10,F"Should royal assent be granted, the
OL,11,Fact will not be commenced until all
OL,12,Frequired secondary legislation and the
OL,13,Fcode of practice have been developed,
OL,14,Fconsulted upon and approved by
OL,15,FTynwald".
OL,17,FIt is thought that the implementation
OL,18,Fperiod for an assisted dying service
OL,19,Fcould be up to two years after royal
OL,20,Fassent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
