FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772100321
OL,3,CPatients face 'considerable' wait for
OL,4,Cassisted dying in Isle of Man
OL,6,FNathan Stilwell, who chairs the
OL,7,FAssisted Dying Coalition, has
OL,8,Fpreviously said Whitehall "should not
OL,9,Fdelay the democratic will" of the
OL,10,FTynwald.
OL,12,FHe said: "every month they stall, more
OL,13,Fdying people are forced to endure
OL,14,Fneedless suffering or travel abroad to
OL,15,Fdie,"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
