PN,39712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772100321
OL,3,CPatients face 'considerable' wait for
OL,4,Cassisted dying in Isle of Man
OL,6,FPoliticians in several parliaments are
OL,7,Fconsidering assisted dying
OL,8,Flegislation, including in Westminster,
OL,9,Fwhere MPs backed the Terminally Ill
OL,10,FAdults (End of Life) Bill 314 votes to
OL,11,F291, majority 23, last June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
